{"tid":2007120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我們別再犯五年前的錯，好嗎？ [2]","createTime":"2020-05-08T07:45:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T06:50:37.000Z","uid":49083,"like":57,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"a0e475322c5a2dfd1629b7bb33e869afd1606351","tid":2007120,"uid":49083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T07:45:14.000Z","msg":"我見舊POST爆左一直無人開番...希望觀賞用巴打唔介意我開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為你個POST真係好好<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1477040/page/1?post=1f62a3ecf3ab58d683a7de7c5d30ab00740cb143\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1477040/page/1?post=1f62a3ecf3ab58d683a7de7c5d30ab00740cb143</a><br />\n<br />\n我見文宣好多都有行動詳情，黑警惡行，還原真相<br />\n我就畫少少關於活動過程中嘅心態<br />\n希望各位任何時候睇返<br />\n可以提醒自己唔好再犯犯過嘅錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有野錯/想加請指出<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t1OGoZu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft1OGoZu.png&h=9fab9b3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不麻木</span><br />\n政府與警方每一次做錯<br />\n都認真對待  不可習慣對方的不公義<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c41gXkX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc41gXkX.png&h=1b0a59eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不要嘉年華</span><br />\n嘉年華式抗爭令活動失焦<br />\n同時觀感不好  被認為玩樂多於抗爭<br />\n亦會逐漸消耗行動意願<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ncc4mOb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNcc4mOb.png&h=61bbca91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">相信前線</span><br />\n不把勇武當冇腦,相信前線能作出明智決定<br />\n不阻撓  不捉鬼<br />\n對家有意要放鬼做事<br />\n一定放鬼直至成功做到為止而且不怕被撿控<br />\n可建議 討論  但請尊重前線最終決定<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7C2sjAw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7C2sjAw.png&h=d01428ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Be water</span><br />\n如水多變  可以是冰是水是蒸汽<br />\n如水轉換   水可成茶可隨器皿改變形狀<br />\n活動形式，行動，撤退時間 必須靈活<br />\n不應拘束過往/現有做法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mNEirgb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmNEirgb.png&h=8f46a8fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不傳謠</span><br />\n所有消息都應經fact check才傳開<br />\n每個消息都要經過思考批判<br />\n不要跌入打了一句「已fact check」<br />\n就一定是真的思考盲點<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4RnsjBu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4RnsjBu.png&h=873d5e7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不要大台</span><br />\n大台只會給予對方明確攻擊目標<br />\n並影響所有示威者行動意願<br />\n更加不要有階段性勝利的想法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wmkBcWT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwmkBcWT.png&h=c43519bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不輕敵</span><br />\n面對對方的狡辯  不應只以嘲笑態度應對<br />\n應憤怒面對 並以文宣反擊<br />\n要想到要明白對方每次狡辯都有無知的人相信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ModftvJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FModftvJ.png&h=a0907e93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不失憶</span><br />\n用盡你整生最記仇最小氣的心態<br />\n去記著對方任何一件錯事  並時時提起<br />\n不再做善忘的香港人 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QOMTZCC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQOMTZCC.png&h=804a2646&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不割席</span><br />\n「掟核彈都唔割」不要只淪為口號<br />\n分化篤灰割席皆是大忌<br />\n用內鬥的時間和精力去做其他事<br />\n只有團結一心才是正確做法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MSFdZD2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMSFdZD2.png&h=bfd387f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我們別再犯五年前的錯，好嗎？"},{"pid":"d770353d07e6a1a9953152a5ab4b9f2be450a39d","tid":2007120,"uid":321421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T07:51:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb5a3aa9b795c476affea7fe9aab8192efc253ae","tid":2007120,"uid":288486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T08:28:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"831411e5a1cf4e81adbe019b5a1b7bc1fa266fc1","tid":2007120,"uid":49083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T09:10:29.000Z","msg":"定期提醒"},{"pid":"505bcdafcbaf6c18fbe079c7c03456f5aa6c995d","tid":2007120,"uid":271176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T09:12:10.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到"},{"pid":"b7ddca6cbeb68ab8ae5bf51c4b9d912d27f77edb","tid":2007120,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T09:18:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69e4922a20ee09f7ed1e3b808e3da72eab5f3b52","tid":2007120,"uid":99528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T09:23:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7cb61cca8ddd5db42c42ac95459d862ddf14cb2e","tid":2007120,"uid":280475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T09:23:51.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"d4e07d984e3494dad034ad20c6f2b889fc1e427c","tid":2007120,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T09:29:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"484b4b531c1fe5f90b0fa347393520cc36dc00b4","tid":2007120,"uid":49083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T13:10:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f91d52014785cbe341ebd6362935b639e2ef7d","tid":2007120,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T14:48:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" 